('6bcbf6eb-87ae-485d-a87f-bc73d4077d70', 'd96624ca-8c7c-4676-a012-87350557ea52', 'Feedback– Your launch strategy should be reviewed by other experienced planters and leaders. They will give you feedback that will improve your plan and save you countless hours of heartache by avoiding problems.', '', 'template', 'c7c589c3-86fb-4c1d-ae75-167df5c79463', 3000, NULL, NULL),
('57b3b49a-e335-490f-ad15-a484412d6156', 'd96624ca-8c7c-4676-a012-87350557ea52', 'Fundraising Tool– Your launch strategy will help you raise funds with potential donors and partners. Simply having a written plan communicates that you have your act together and MAY be worthy of a donor’s trust. Ultimately, your vision and passion will s', 'Fundraising Tool– Your launch strategy will help you raise funds with potential donors and partners. Simply having a written plan communicates that you have your act together and MAY be worthy of a donor’s trust. Ultimately, your vision and passion will sell your plan. The written launch strategy is a tool for opening the door to further discussions with donors.', 'template', 'c7c589c3-86fb-4c1d-ae75-167df5c79463', 4000, NULL, NULL),
