('d4c7fc85-979b-405d-9599-e66efc43b567', 'd0effbb3-5688-4828-862f-f35ecca1647f', 'Local Neighborhood Events – These events are very simple and can be done with minimal planning and cost (less than $200 each). They will usually impact 50 or less people at a time. For example, a backyard BBQ is a very easy event that every staff member a', 'Local Neighborhood Events – These events are very simple and can be done with minimal planning and cost (less than $200 each). They will usually impact 50 or less people at a time. For example, a backyard BBQ is a very easy event that every staff member and launch team member should be willing to plan and host. These events provide the opportunity for very personal invitations to friends, neighbors, co-workers, etc. These are small, more intimate events that are easy to plan and should be done locally by each staff member and launch team member.', 'template', 'c7c589c3-86fb-4c1d-ae75-167df5c79463', 1000, NULL, NULL),
('1fa249cf-bd61-4a88-8a01-6c2f88c1668c', 'd0effbb3-5688-4828-862f-f35ecca1647f', 'Community-Wide Events – These events require more planning or cost (up to $1000) and will likely impact 25-250 people. For example, a community concert hosted at a local park should attract over 100 people with minimal planning and cost (especially if the', 'Community-Wide Events – These events require more planning or cost (up to $1000) and will likely impact 25-250 people. For example, a community concert hosted at a local park should attract over 100 people with minimal planning and cost (especially if the church band plays). Another example is a parenting seminar on a Saturday morning featuring a special speaker and hosted in a local day care facility. Marketing/promoting these events is more extensive than for neighborhood events and includes flyers, signs, newsletter ads, invitations sent home with kids, etc.', 'template', 'c7c589c3-86fb-4c1d-ae75-167df5c79463', 2000, NULL, NULL),
('7a5bdfe7-4555-4655-b95d-429438031763', 'd0effbb3-5688-4828-862f-f35ecca1647f', 'Regional Events – These events are very large events which have the ability to impact hundreds or even thousands of people. These events require a great deal of planning and budgeting, probably well over the $1000 community event described above. For exam', 'Regional Events – These events are very large events which have the ability to impact hundreds or even thousands of people. These events require a great deal of planning and budgeting, probably well over the $1000 community event described above. For example, a city wide carnival featuring free games, food, pony rides, clowns/mascots, face-painting, and multiple inflatable rides/amusements. These events receive maximum publicity and marketing including flyers, signs, newspaper ads, newsletter ads, direct mail, radio or other mass means (free public service announcements), etc. The best regional events involve partnering with local civic and community organizations including elected politicians.', 'template', 'c7c589c3-86fb-4c1d-ae75-167df5c79463', 3000, NULL, NULL),
